arStrings.szText:
{c_important}Resolute Tributes reward only the Player who offers the Tribute.{/c}

Only usable in Torment Difficulties.

Offer to the Undercity's Spirit Brazier to enhance its rewards:
{icon:bullet,1.2} Completing the dungeon with at least Attunement Rank 1 will reward several Uniques, with an increased chance of a Mythic Unique.
